            "md": "<p><a href=\"http://github.com/badges/stability-badges\"><img src=\"http://badges.github.io/stability-badges/dist/stable.svg\" alt=\"stable\"></a></p>\n<p>Converts GB disk size into a more readable format (e.g. GBs, TBs)</p>\n",
